A CIA hitman decides to complete one final mission after he learns that a dangerous terrorist is on American soil, but soon discovers that he is also a target. SHARPSHOOTER stars James Remar (DEXTER), Mario Van Peebles (ALI), Catherine Mary Stewart (WEEKEND AT BERNIE?S), and Bruce Boxleitner (BABYLON 5) as Sheriff Garner.

When an assassin working for the CIA decides to take one final job before retiring he finds himself the target in a deadly terrorist plot.

Special Ops sniper and ex-navy SEAL, Dillon, has put it all on the line for one last mission of utmost importance to national security. A well-known terrorist has settled in the US with plans to sell nuclear materials to North Korea. He must be stopped.

Forced to abandon his plan to infiltrate the terrorist cell, Dillon retreats to the woods to regroup and consider his options. He soon discovers that he is now the target and a team of highly trained men are in pursuit of him. Who has set a trap for him  - and why?
